    "This relationship, exemplified in the context of ChatGPT, grammatical agency, and social agency, builds on prior research on the social agency of decision-making algorithms [18,60,61,65,82].",
    "Hence, our investigation significantly adds to the understanding of the social impact of ChatGPT, employing a combination of CL and CDA, underpinned by SAR.",
